title: 267: How Our Christmas Traditions Have Changed Throughout The Years | Ear Biscuits Ep.267
description:
Christmas may look a little different for everyone this year, but for R&L, there have been 3 distinct phases (and one phase of Christmases yet to come) of how they've viewed and celebrated Christmas throughout their years. Listen to the guys discuss their Christmas traditions past, present, and future in this episode of Ear Biscuits!
